Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview
   2. Dependencies

        2.1. External Libraries or Applications

   3. Parameters

        3.1. host (str)
        3.2. port (int)
        3.3. keepalive (int)
        3.4. id (str)
        3.5. username (str)
        3.6. password (str)
        3.7. will_topic (str)
        3.8. will (str)
        3.9. event_callback (str)

   4. Functions

        4.1. mqtt_subscribe(topic, qos)
        4.2. mqtt_unsubscribe(topic)
        4.3. mqtt_publish(topic, message, qos)

